===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''''Bryophyta'''''
#{{botany}}: a [[botanical name]], at any rank above that of family.  [[Circumscription]] and placement of such a taxon depend on [[taxonomic system]] and viewpoint. 
::- for example within [[kingdom]] ''[[Plantae]]'' - the [[moss]]es, [[liverwort]]s, and [[hornwort]]s. This circumscription is often regarded as obsolete
#{{botany}}: a [[botanical name]] at the rank of [[division]] or [[phylum]].  [[Circumscription]] and placement of this [[division]] or [[phylum]] depend on [[taxonomic system]] and viewpoint. 
::- commonly the [[moss]]es

